        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Name the Enemy Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the federal government from creating documents that refer to China's head of state as anything other than <i>General Secretary of the Central Committee of the Chinese Communist Party </i>or <i>General Secretary</i>.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
